Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,凱文·科斯特納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,安迪·加西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:05.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,羅伯特·德·尼祿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:10.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,肖恩·康納利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:22.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fn華文楷體}片名: 鐵面無私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:54.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,1930年 禁酒令使芝加哥變成戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,幫派人物爭地盤搶權力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,建立億萬元計的私酒王國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們用暴力手段來鞏固他們的勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:06.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是一個無法紀的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:11.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,梟雄 艾爾·卡彭 不可一世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:25.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,An article, which I believe appeared in a newspaper, asked why,\N{\rCHT}艾爾 報紙上有篇文章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:29.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,since it would seem that you are in effect the Mayor of Chicago,\N{\rCHT}事實上你等於是芝加哥市長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:34.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,you're not simply being appointed to that position.\N{\rCHT}你只是差一紙委任令而己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:41.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I tell ya, it's touching. Like a lot of things in life,\N{\rCHT}我告訴你 這很動人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:46.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,we laugh because it's funny, and we laugh because it's true.\N{\rCHT}有許多事可笑 因為那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Some people say, reformers here say:\N{\rCHT}有些人說:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:52.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Put that man in jail, what does he think he is doing? "\N{\rCHT}拿那人下獄 他自以為他在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:56.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What I hope I'm doing, and here's where your paper's got a point,\N{\rCHT}同樣的 我在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,is I'm responding to the will of the people.\N{\rCHT}你們報紙要弄清楚 我是在反映民眾意見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:06.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,People are gonna drink. We all know that. All I do is act on that.\N{\rCHT}人們要喝酒 你知道我知道 大家都知道 我只是知而後行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,And all this talk of bootlegging. What is bootlegging?\N{\rCHT}說什麼販賣私酒? 什麼叫販賣私酒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:13.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,On the boat it's bootlegging, on Lake Shore Drive it's hospitality.\N{\rCHT}我不是在賣私酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm a businessman.\N{\rCHT}我只是個生意人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:21.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your reputation is that you control your business through violence.\N{\rCHT}你以暴力控制生意 怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:26.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,That those that don't purchase your product are dealt with violently.\N{\rCHT}把你的貨強迫推銷出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\N{\rCHT}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I grew up in a tough neighbourhood.\N{\rCHT}我在惡劣環境下長大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:39.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,We used to say, "You can get further with a kind word and a gun"\N{\rCHT}我們常說:槍桿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,"than you can with just a kind word."\N{\rCHT}勝過許多好話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,And in that neighbourhood it might've been true.\N{\rCHT}在我那種環境這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,And sometimes your reputation follows you.\N{\rCHT}然後你會贏得名謄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,There is violence in Chicago, but not by me\N{\rCHT}芝加哥的確有暴力存在 但並不在於我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:59.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,and not by anybody I employ. Because it's not good business.\N{\rCHT}或是我雇用的人 我告訴你們原因? 因為那不是好生意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:34.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leave us alone down here, we've got everything we need.\N{\rCHT}走開 不要打攪我們 我們不需要任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,The green beer you're peddling aingt any good.\N{\rCHT}你那些東西毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:42.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not supposed to be good. It's supposed to be bought.\N{\rCHT}很有用的 很值得一買
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not buying any.\N{\rCHT}我什麼也不買
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:52.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Pops, we won't come back.\N{\rCHT}別擔心 我們不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:58.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,How's everyone at your house today? They're fine.\N{\rCHT}你家裡的人都好嗎 他們很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:02.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is your Mama well? She has a little cold.\N{\rCHT}你媽好呢 她有點感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, she does?\N{\rCHT}是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that. But she'll be all right.\N{\rCHT}我很難過聽到這事 她不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,There you go. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}給你 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:22.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all right, sweetie. You be careful crossing the street.\N{\rCHT}不客氣 小可愛 過馬路時要當心 告訴你媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mister! You tell your Mama that...\N{\rCHT}先生…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister! Wait!\N{\rCHT}先生 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mister! Wait! You forgot your brief...\N{\rCHT}先生 等一下 你忘了你的手提箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,“私酒戰爭屠殺十歲女孩”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:41.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard it on the radio.\N{\rCHT}是的 我聽到收音機廣播了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\rCHT}我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:47.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to go to work.\N{\rCHT}上班時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:58.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll make a good first impression.\N{\rCHT}你要給人第一眼好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you, Eliot.\N{\rCHT}我愛你 艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, shoo.\N{\rCHT}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:23.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eliot Ness, Special Agent of the Treasury Department.\N{\rCHT}艾略特.奈斯 財政部特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness. Thank you, Chief.\N{\rCHT}奈斯 謝謝你 局長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,At the request of the City of Chicago,\N{\rCHT}基於芝加哥市民要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:33.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,the Department of the Treasury has inaugurated a programme\N{\rCHT}聯邦政府令財政部成立專案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,to deal with the flow of illegal liquor and the violence it creates.\N{\rCHT}制止私酒之販賣及其所引發之暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness! Of what does this programme consist?\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 這個計畫包括什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,I and other agents of the Treasury will be working\N{\rCHT}我和其它財政部專員將與
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,with the Chicago Police...\N{\rCHT}警方及其它單位合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just another showpiece programme?\N{\rCHT}這是否又是一次官樣文章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:53.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think of prohibition? Do you drink, Mr Ness?\N{\rCHT}你對禁酒令有何看法 你喝不喝酒? 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:57.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, answer the questions. It's not just a showpiece.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 回答問題 這不是官樣文章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:01.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you how I feel about prohibition.\N{\rCHT}我來告訴你們 我對禁酒令的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is the law of the land.\N{\rCHT}那是國家的法律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you consider yourself a crusader, is that it?\N{\rCHT}你自認你是位掃蕩戰士嗎? 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,What qualifications do you have for the job?\N{\rCHT}你有何專長擔此大任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you have any political ambitions?\N{\rCHT}你可有政治野心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, boys, I think that's enough.\N{\rCHT}好了 今天到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are your real plans? What have you got coming up?\N{\rCHT}你有何計畫? 打算如何著手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll have to read about it in the paper.\N{\rCHT}你去看報紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:25.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me ride along with you. No. Can't help you.\N{\rCHT}讓我和你同去 我們會配合得很好 不 愛莫能助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:29.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness, Lieutenant Alderson, the Flying Squad.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 奧德森中尉 飛騎警隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to meet the men?\N{\rCHT}你準備會見弟兄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.\N{\rCHT}是的 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,“預備室武器登記”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have one more thing to say.\N{\rCHT}我還有一件事要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know that many of you take a drink.\N{\rCHT}我知道你們很多人喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:59.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,What you've done before today is not my concern.\N{\rCHT}今天以前的事我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:03.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,But now we must be pure, and I want you to stop.\N{\rCHT}但今後要乾淨 停止喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:09.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not a question of whether it's 'a harmless drink'. It may well be.\N{\rCHT}問題不在於喝酒是否傷身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,But it's against the law.\N{\rCHT}而在於那是違反法律 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:15.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,And as we are going to enforce the law, we must do first by example.\N{\rCHT}我們要厲行法律便要以身作則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are there any questions?\N{\rCHT}有疑問嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:27.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good. The Department of the Treasury's had\N{\rCHT}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,a man undercover here for some time now.\N{\rCHT}財政部有位密探臥底一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've received word from this informant\N{\rCHT}我們接獲情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,that a large shipment of Canadian whiskey has arrived in Chicago.\N{\rCHT}昨天自加拿大運來了大批私酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I hope that you have signed on for some action.\N{\rCHT}所以我希望你們準備一下 我們要去抓他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:51.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remember, the liquor cases are marked with the red maple leaf.\N{\rCHT}記住私酒箱上有紅色記號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:55.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Treasury Agent is in a grey suit with a white scarf.\N{\rCHT}密探穿的是灰大衣白圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:59.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,He is not to be arrested. A grey suit and a white scarf.\N{\rCHT}不要抓他 灰大衣 白圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:04.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's it. Are your men ready? Yes, sir. They are.\N{\rCHT}就這樣 你的人準備好了嗎 是的 先生 都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,At ease. Smoke 'em if you got 'em.\N{\rCHT}稍息 準備對付壞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,How are we doing Okay.\N{\rCHT}準備如何? 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:33.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Want part of a sandwich? No, thank you, sir.\N{\rCHT}來點三明治 不 謝謝 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:42.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,You nervous? No, sir.\N{\rCHT}你緊張嗎 不 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:48.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Been with the unit long? A short while.\N{\rCHT}你在這單位很久了 才一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:53.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,I suppose we all want to do well. Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}我想大家都想把事做好 是的 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,A message from my wife.\N{\rCHT}我太太寫的字條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,You married? Yes, sir, I am.\N{\rCHT}你結婚了? 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nice to be married, huh?\N{\rCHT}結婚不錯 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:28.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just follow me.\N{\rCHT}跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God... Federal officer. Hands in the air.\N{\rCHT}聯邦官員 手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get 'em up. Drop it.\N{\rCHT}聯邦官員 手舉起來 東西放下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I can't, it'll break.\N{\rCHT}我不能 會砸壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness. Look, I was just...\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:24.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Geez, I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:30.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, I can do a lot for you, what you're trying to do.\N{\rCHT}聽著 我可以為你做許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I get the big scoop, you make a big splash.\N{\rCHT}我搶大新聞 替你宣揚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:37.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get some support. What do you say? Let's be real, let me help you.\N{\rCHT}爭取新聞界支持如何? 讓我幫你 如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just shut up.\N{\rCHT}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:09.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right now... Let's do some good!\N{\rCHT}好了 各位 我們大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!\N{\rCHT}站住別動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:31.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Federal officer. You're under arrest for violations of the Volstead Act.\N{\rCHT}聯邦官員 你們因違反禁酒令被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's cover the doors! Don't let anybody out!\N{\rCHT}關上門 誰都不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Preseuski.\N{\rCHT}普勒斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm here with permission. Who gave you permission?\N{\rCHT}借過 借過 我有許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:55.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness! Sorry, let him through here.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 不要緊 讓他進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let him through here.\N{\rCHT}讓他進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want to take your picture, take it now.\N{\rCHT}你要拍照就現在拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,You ready? Ready.\N{\rCHT}你要拍照就現在拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:39.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get him out of here.\N{\rCHT}帶他出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:43.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tear the place apart! I mean now, get him out!\N{\rCHT}把這兒拆散 現在 帶他出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,That means you, too.\N{\rCHT}你也出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,“緝酒戰士奈斯灰頭土臉”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,“差勁的艾略特.奈斯”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,“我非常以你為榮”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:19.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, what do you think you're doing?\N{\rCHT}你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:24.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want to throw garbage? Throw it in the goddamn trash basket.\N{\rCHT}要丟垃圾丟到垃圾袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't you have more important things to do?\N{\rCHT}你沒有更重要的事做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:33.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.But I'm not doing them right now.\N{\rCHT}有 但我不必現在去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do we understand each other?\N{\rCHT}我們彼此都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, pal, why the Mohaska?\N{\rCHT}好了 朋友 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:48.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why are you packing the gun? I'm a Treasury Officer.\N{\rCHT}你為何帶著槍 我是財政部特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:57.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.Just remember what we talked about now.\N{\rCHT}好吧 我沒空和你閒扯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey... Wait a minute!\N{\rCHT}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:07.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell kind of police do you have in this goddamn city?\N{\rCHT}這個城市的員警是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You just turned your back on an armed man.\N{\rCHT}你竟背對著位帶槍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:14.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a Treasury officer. I just told you I was.\N{\rCHT}你是位財政部官員 何以見得 那只是我說的而己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who would claim to be that, who was not?\N{\rCHT}誰願冒充財政部官員 除了瘋子外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's your name and unit?\N{\rCHT}你的姓名和單位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's right here.\N{\rCHT}在這上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a beef? What is it?\N{\rCHT}你有牢騷 怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,How did you know I had a gun?\N{\rCHT}你怎麼知道我有帶槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you want, a free lesson in police work?\N{\rCHT}你要什麼? 學會員警的絕招嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, pal?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧? 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,I had a rough day on the job.\N{\rCHT}我工作不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:06.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you going home now? I was about to.\N{\rCHT}你要回家了嗎 我正要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:13.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, then, you just fulfilled the first rule of law enforcement.\N{\rCHT}你已做到了執法者規則第一條
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:21.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Make sure when your shift is over you go home alive.\N{\rCHT}確保能活著下班回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:24.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here endeth the lesson.\N{\rCHT}第一課結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:27.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,$100, 000 for 40 barrels. Make sure there are no empties.\N{\rCHT}總數十萬元 一共四十桶 別有空的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:30.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give you the ledger, everything is in the book.\N{\rCHT}我給你的底帳都在帳簿裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,55 gallons to the barrel.\N{\rCHT}桶是五十五加侖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:50.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Eddie. Come in, Eddie.\N{\rCHT}我是艾迪 進來 艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,“緝酒戰士奈斯灰頭土臉”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:20.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, he gets into the snowplough, and he says, "Let's do some good".\N{\rCHT}他坐進除雪車裡說道 “我們好好幹一場”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then, we bust through...\N{\rCHT}然後我們破門而入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:52.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,“緝酒戰士奈斯灰頭土臉”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:15.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness? Yes?\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生? 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:18.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I came here to thank you.\N{\rCHT}我是來謝謝你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:24.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was...my little girl that got killed with that bomb.\N{\rCHT}被炸死的小女孩是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:27.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please.\N{\rCHT}我很難過 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm...l'm so sorry.\N{\rCHT}我很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,You see, it's...because I know that you have children, too.\N{\rCHT}你瞭解 因為我知道你也有小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:44.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that this is real for you, that these men cause us tragedy.\N{\rCHT}你會真心認為這是件悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:48.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I know that you will put a stop to them.\N{\rCHT}你要阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:51.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you do that, now.\N{\rCHT}你要阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you want? I'd like to talk to you.\N{\rCHT}你要幹什麼 我想和你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.63,0:23:55.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come in.\N{\rCHT}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:02.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need a small group of men, handpicked, starting with you.\N{\rCHT}我要找一批人 首先找上的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:06.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ness! I am just a poor beat cop.\N{\rCHT}奈斯 奈斯 我只是個可憐的巡夜員警
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.31,0:24:12.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, how can I help you? Just work with me.\N{\rCHT}我如何能幫助你 只要和我一起辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,But why should I, though? Because you're a good cop.\N{\rCHT}我為什麼要 因為你是好員警
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:20.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you know that? You told me.\N{\rCHT}你怎麼知道 你告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:24.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,If I'm such a good cop...\N{\rCHT}我若是好員警
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:28.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,How come I'm walking the beat, then, at my age?\N{\rCHT}我還會在這年紀仍擔任巡夜嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:30.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you want to tell me?\N{\rCHT}你想告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.46,0:24:33.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I'm that Whore with a Heart of Gold.\N{\rCHT}也許我是心地善良
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.55,0:24:37.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Or The One Good Cop in the Bad Town? Is that what you want to hear?\N{\rCHT}罪惡圈裡唯一的好員警 你想聽這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:39.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you, and I don't care!\N{\rCHT}我沒要求你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.72,0:24:43.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want to stay on the beat? You do that.\N{\rCHT}我不在乎 你要去巡夜就請便
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:48.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to come with me, I need your help.\N{\rCHT}你願跟我一起嗎? 我需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:51.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you for help.\N{\rCHT}我在請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.78,0:24:59.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well...that's the thing you fear, isn't it?\N{\rCHT}你害怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:08.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness, I wish I'd met you ten years and...twenty pounds ago.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 希望在十年前就遇到你 或是體重輕二十磅前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.87,0:25:16.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,But...I just think it got... more important to me...to stay alive.\N{\rCHT}現在對我較重要的便是保住老命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.80,0:25:28.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm walking the beat. Thank you, no.\N{\rCHT}所以我甘心擔任巡夜 謝謝 我不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:45.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's good, Andy. Let's start up the thing and take a little ride.\N{\rCHT}來 開車吧 我們去兜風
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.99,0:25:48.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear that Stutz Bearcat engine, boy!\N{\rCHT}我要聽一下熊貓牌引擎的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.75,0:25:52.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let me open the door here. Yeah, go ahead.\N{\rCHT}好 讓我開車門 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.29,0:25:55.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoopsy daisy, pick up the door there, Andy.\N{\rCHT}你快去把門撿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:26:00.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Throw it in the back seat. Now, let me get the thing started.\N{\rCHT}把它扔到後座 讓我發動引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.05,0:26:02.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, start it up, Andy.\N{\rCHT}對 發動引擎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.06,0:26:12.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy mackerel, Andy! Listen to that Bearcat motor!\N{\rCHT}天啊! 聽聽引擎聲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.35,0:26:17.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it sounds like the bear is chasing that cat all round it!\N{\rCHT}聽起來就像大熊不停追著小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.78,0:26:20.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Andy! She's boiling over!\N{\rCHT}引擎過熱冒煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.83,0:26:34.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness? Yes.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.96,0:26:37.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oscar Wallace.\N{\rCHT}奧斯卡.華萊士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.21,0:26:42.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been assigned here by the Washington Bureau.\N{\rCHT}華盛頓派我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.51,0:26:44.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Really? Yes.\N{\rCHT}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.97,0:26:49.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad to have you here, Mr Wallace. Would you excuse me?\N{\rCHT}我很高興你加入…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.77,0:26:53.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,We are a little in the dark here, but any ideas you may have...\N{\rCHT}我們現在一籌莫展 你有建議嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.81,0:26:55.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, yes, sir, I do.\N{\rCHT}是的 我有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.98,0:27:00.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,And the one I want to try first... is this.\N{\rCHT}我首先要試的便是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.45,0:27:07.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,He has not filed a return since 1926.\N{\rCHT}他自1926年就沒有申報過
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.08,0:27:12.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,A return...? An income tax return.\N{\rCHT}申報 申報所得稅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.25,0:27:15.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Income tax. Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}申報所得稅? 是的 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.96,0:27:20.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you do at the Bureau? Oh, I'm an accountant.\N{\rCHT}你在局裡是做什麼的 華萊士我是會計
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.46,0:27:25.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,An accountant? Yes, and the Bureau sent me here...\N{\rCHT}會計? 是的 總局派我來此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.68,0:27:29.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you excuse me?\N{\rCHT}失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.22,0:27:34.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please.\N{\rCHT}坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.21,0:28:02.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.\N{\rCHT}好了 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.88,0:28:07.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are we going? These walls have ears.\N{\rCHT}去哪裡 這裡隔牆有耳
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:13.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to know how to get Capone.\N{\rCHT}你說你想知道 如何扳倒卡彭
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:20.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to get him? You see what I'm saying?\N{\rCHT}你真的要捉他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.65,0:28:25.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you prepared to do? Everything within the law.\N{\rCHT}你明白我的意思 你打算怎麼做? 一切合法的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.47,0:28:28.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then what are you prepared to do?\N{\rCHT}若不成 你又有何打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.36,0:28:31.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you open the ball on these people,\N{\rCHT}如果你打算向他們開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.20,0:28:33.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,you must be prepared to go all the way.\N{\rCHT}你就要一直戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.95,0:28:37.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because they won't give up the fight until one of you is dead.\N{\rCHT}因為他們非和你拼個你死我活不可
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.33,0:28:39.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to get Capone. I don't know how.\N{\rCHT}我要捉卡彭 我不知該如何下手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.62,0:28:44.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here's how you get Capone: he pulls a knife, you pull a gun.\N{\rCHT}要捉卡彭 就要比他強他拔刀 你就拔槍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.71,0:28:47.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,He sends one of yours to hospital, you send one of his to the morgue!\N{\rCHT}他傷了你的部下 你就宰了他的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.70,0:28:51.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the Chicago way! And that's how you get Capone.\N{\rCHT}那就是芝加哥的規則 那就是捉卡彭的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.60,0:28:57.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, do you want to do that?\N{\rCHT}你能那樣幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.02,0:28:59.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to do that?\N{\rCHT}你準備好那樣幹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:05.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm making you a deal. Do you want this deal?\N{\rCHT}我提供你這建議 你要不要接受?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.40,0:29:09.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have sworn to put this man away,\N{\rCHT}我已發誓要將他繩之以法
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.03,0:29:14.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,with any and all legal means at my disposal, and I will do so.\N{\rCHT}以合法手段 盡我所能去達成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.04,0:29:25.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, the Lord hates a coward.\N{\rCHT}天主憎惡懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.55,0:29:35.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a blood oath is, Mr Ness?\N{\rCHT}你可知血誓之意義
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.97,0:29:39.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. Good. 'Cause you just took one.\N{\rCHT}是的 很好 你剛得了個宣過血誓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.98,0:29:44.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you think Capone knew about your raid the other night?\N{\rCHT}你明白那晚的突襲何以不成功?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.40,0:29:48.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somebody on the cops told him. Right. Welcome to Chicago.\N{\rCHT}有人通風報信 對 你開竅了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.24,0:29:51.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,This town stinks like a whorehouse at low tide.\N{\rCHT}芝加哥就像娼館一樣污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.91,0:29:56.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,First, who can you trust? Nobody. The cops, nobody.\N{\rCHT}首先的是 你能相信誰 沒有人 員警? 沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.62,0:30:01.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,'Cause nobody wants you here. Then why are you helping me?\N{\rCHT}這裡沒有人喜歡你 那你為何肯幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.58,0:30:04.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because I swore to uphold the law.\N{\rCHT}因為我曾宣誓維護法律執行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.79,0:30:07.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,And if you believe that, I'll tell you another.\N{\rCHT}你要相信的話 我再告訴你另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.84,0:30:12.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, who can you trust? I can trust nobody.\N{\rCHT}你能信任誰? 我誰也不信任
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.30,0:30:16.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the sorry truth. Then, where are we gonna get help?\N{\rCHT}那是件悲哀的事 我們誰也不能信任的話要如何取得幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.60,0:30:21.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you're afraid of getting a rotten apple, don't go to the barrel.\N{\rCHT}如果你不想拿到爛蘋果 那就別拿桶子裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.67,0:30:24.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get it off the tree.\N{\rCHT}去摘樹上的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.06,0:30:26.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get it off the tree...\N{\rCHT}去樹上摘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:32.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Finger out of the trigger guard! Eject those cartridges!\N{\rCHT}手放在扳機罩 彈出彈夾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.24,0:30:35.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lay the revolver on the ledge and stand back!\N{\rCHT}放下左輪 退後一步
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.62,0:30:37.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,About face!\N{\rCHT}向後轉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:41.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Barry! I want you to meet Mr Eliot Ness.\N{\rCHT}賴特 見過艾略特.奈斯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.20,0:30:45.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Treasury Department. How are you? We need a recruit for extended duty.\N{\rCHT}財政部特派員 你好 我們需要人手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.21,0:30:50.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,He is to be seconded to the Treasury Department. We have the full...\N{\rCHT}我們有財政部的公文要求協助
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.05,0:30:53.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Barry? Who is consistently the best shot of this class?\N{\rCHT}這班上誰的射擊成績最好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.51,0:30:58.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Williamson and Stone. Call them out, one at a time.\N{\rCHT}威廉森和斯通 好 替我叫他們來好嗎 一次一位
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.64,0:31:01.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are either of the men married? No.\N{\rCHT}請問他們是否結婚了? 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.27,0:31:04.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good. Williamson!\N{\rCHT}威廉森
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.06,0:31:08.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're married. I don't want any married men.\N{\rCHT}你可是結過婚了 我不要結過婚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:13.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, stand easy, son. I want to ask you something.\N{\rCHT}好了 稍息 小夥子 我有些話問你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.49,0:31:18.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to join the force? To protect and...\N{\rCHT}你為何投考警校 為了保護
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:21.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,To protect and serve... To protect and...\N{\rCHT}為了保護…服務
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.04,0:31:25.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please don't search for the yearbook answer. Just tell me what you think.\N{\rCHT}別背書上的答案 告訴我你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.42,0:31:28.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,What I think? I... You...\N{\rCHT}我的想法 我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.63,0:31:31.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,...could help...the force.\N{\rCHT}…可以幫助…警方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.63,0:31:35.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can help... With the force.\N{\rCHT}你可以幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.97,0:31:40.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you. There goes the next Chief of Police.\N{\rCHT}好了 謝謝 未來的局長人選
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.19,0:31:48.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,At ease!\N{\rCHT}稍息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.90,0:31:52.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone! Out here.\N{\rCHT}斯通 出來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.69,0:31:56.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,This kid's a prodigy.\N{\rCHT}這小子是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.49,0:32:02.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to join the force? To protect the property and...\N{\rCHT}你為何加入員警行列 為了保護人民財產
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.95,0:32:06.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, don't waste my time with that bullshit.\N{\rCHT}請別說廢話 浪費我的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:10.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are you from, Stone?\N{\rCHT}你是哪裡人? 斯通
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.42,0:32:14.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,From the Southside. Stone?\N{\rCHT}南方人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.97,0:32:18.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,George Stone, that's your name?\N{\rCHT}斯通 喬治.斯通是你本名嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.72,0:32:24.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's your real name? That is my real name.\N{\rCHT}你的真名是什麼 那就是我的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.02,0:32:26.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nah! What was it before you changed it?\N{\rCHT}不是 在你改名換姓前叫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.15,0:32:33.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Giuseppe Petri. Geez, I knew it!\N{\rCHT}喬瑟比班達 我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.28,0:32:36.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all you need, one thieving wop on the team!\N{\rCHT}我早就說過隊上有壞分子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.36,0:32:39.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's that you said?\N{\rCHT}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.24,0:32:43.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said that you're a lying member of a no-good race.\N{\rCHT}我說你撒謊 是個敗類
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.91,0:32:49.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's much better than you, you stinking Irish pig.\N{\rCHT}比你好多了 你這愛爾蘭臭豬
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.88,0:32:53.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, I like him.\N{\rCHT}我喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.26,0:32:58.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like him, too.\N{\rCHT}我也喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.01,0:33:02.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,You just joined the Treasury Department, son.\N{\rCHT}你剛加入了財政部小夥子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.26,0:33:05.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.\N{\rCHT}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.64,0:33:08.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eliot Ness.\N{\rCHT}艾略特.奈斯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.98,0:33:13.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,With reports from stake-outs on the North and West side, and...\N{\rCHT}我們從西區和北區接獲報告
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.11,0:33:16.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lieutenant. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝 警官 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.24,0:33:25.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\N{\rCHT}你覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.41,0:33:28.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think there's nothing like vaudeville.\N{\rCHT}像雜耍團的小丑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.87,0:33:33.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's what I think. Now, are you ready to go to work?\N{\rCHT}我也是這樣想 現在 你們準備好去辦事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.92,0:33:37.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are we going? On a liquor raid.\N{\rCHT}去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.67,0:33:39.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need another man.\N{\rCHT}去突檢私酒 我們還少個人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.67,0:33:42.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness? This is very interesting.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 這很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.09,0:33:46.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've found a financial disbursement pattern which shows some irregu...\N{\rCHT}我發現財政部的紀錄上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.39,0:33:48.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,You carry a badge? Yes.\N{\rCHT}你有警證嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.56,0:33:50.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Carry a gun.\N{\rCHT}拿支槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.16,0:34:09.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jimmy...? What?\N{\rCHT}吉米 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.75,0:34:14.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you dressed for? Hallowe'en?\N{\rCHT}你穿那樣是幹什麼? 萬聖節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.63,0:34:16.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shut up. I'm working.\N{\rCHT}閉嘴 我在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.71,0:34:18.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where? The circus?\N{\rCHT}哪兒? 馬戲團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.82,0:34:42.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are. What are we doing here?\N{\rCHT}就是這裡 我們來這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.78,0:34:45.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Liquor raid.\N{\rCHT}突檢私酒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.70,0:34:48.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here? !\N{\rCHT}這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.24,0:34:52.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows where the booze is. The problem isn't finding it.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 大家都知道私酒在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.75,0:34:57.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,The problem is who wants to cross Capone. Let's go.\N{\rCHT}問題不在於找出私酒 而在於誰敢招惹卡彭 我們進去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.89,0:35:07.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'd better be damn sure, Malone.\N{\rCHT}你最好確定是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.31,0:35:17.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you walk through this door, you're walking into a world of trouble.\N{\rCHT}一進入此門你就是走進麻煩之中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.86,0:35:21.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back. Do you understand?\N{\rCHT}不能回頭 你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.03,0:35:22.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.\N{\rCHT}是的 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.45,0:35:26.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good. Give me that axe.\N{\rCHT}好 把斧頭給我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.66,0:35:37.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Federal officers! Get your hands in the air!\N{\rCHT}聯邦官員 手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.71,0:35:40.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody moves! This is a raid!\N{\rCHT}不准動 突擊檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.09,0:35:43.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everybody... What are you doing here?\N{\rCHT}你們是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.42,0:35:47.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,All this stuff is impounded! You're all under arrest!\N{\rCHT}所有的物品都充公 你們全被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.39,0:35:51.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey! This isn't right! Hey! This is no good!\N{\rCHT}這樣不對
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.39,0:35:55.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a warrant? Sure! Here's my warrant.\N{\rCHT}你們可有拘捕令 這就是拘票
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.65,0:35:59.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you think he feels now? Better...or worse?\N{\rCHT}你們現在認為他感覺好些還是不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.49,0:36:11.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is that? What is that?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.08,0:36:14.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it? God, I'm with a heathen.\N{\rCHT}那是什麼? 你不信教嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.45,0:36:19.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,That is my callbox key. And that is Saint Jude.\N{\rCHT}那是我的鑰匙鏈 那個是聖猶大
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.67,0:36:24.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Il Santo Jude. He's the patron saint of lost causes.\N{\rCHT}猶大是失敗者的守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:27.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,And policemen.\N{\rCHT}他也守護員警
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.22,0:36:31.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Patron saint of policemen? Everybody needs a friend.\N{\rCHT}員警的守護神 每個人都需要朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.85,0:36:36.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lost causes, policemen...\N{\rCHT}失敗和員警
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.35,0:36:40.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Which do you want to be? I want to be a cop.\N{\rCHT}你想當哪一種 我想當員警
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.15,0:36:42.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,You do? Yes.\N{\rCHT}是嗎? 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.19,0:36:44.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why?\N{\rCHT}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.61,0:36:49.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,'T o protect the property and the citizenry...'\N{\rCHT}為了保護市民生命財產
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.91,0:36:53.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's all right.\N{\rCHT}沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.99,0:36:56.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? ! I got to tell you, congratulations!\N{\rCHT}你幹嘛? 我只是來恭賀你們
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.71,0:37:00.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay if I get a picture of you and your men?\N{\rCHT}我可以替你們拍張照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.71,0:37:03.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But not for publication. Just for us!\N{\rCHT}好 但不能發表 只能給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.80,0:37:06.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anything you say, Mr Ness.\N{\rCHT}聽你的 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.63,0:37:10.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Closer in... Oh, that's great. Okay, ready? Hold it.\N{\rCHT}看這裡 好了 預備
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.39,0:37:21.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Life goes on.\N{\rCHT}日子要過下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.07,0:37:29.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,A man becomes preeminent, he's expected to have enthusiasms.\N{\rCHT}人們期望卓越的人有熱忱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.43,0:37:31.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Enthusiasms...\N{\rCHT}熱忱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.62,0:37:35.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Enthusiasms...\N{\rCHT}熱忱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.70,0:37:38.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are mine?\N{\rCHT}我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.66,0:37:43.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,What draws my admiration? What is that which gives me joy?\N{\rCHT}我熱衷什麼 什麼能使我高興?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.88,0:37:47.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dames! Boozing\N{\rCHT}美女…喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.80,0:37:52.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Baseball!\N{\rCHT}棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.18,0:38:00.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,A man...\N{\rCHT}一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.85,0:38:04.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,A man stands alone at the plate.\N{\rCHT}一個人上場打球時
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.23,0:38:09.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the time for what?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.78,0:38:12.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,For individual achievement.\N{\rCHT}一個人的成就時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.03,0:38:16.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,There he stands alone.\N{\rCHT}他單獨站在那
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.33,0:38:19.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,But in the field, what?\N{\rCHT}在場上有些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.71,0:38:23.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Part of a team.\N{\rCHT}球隊的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.83,0:38:26.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Teamwork...\N{\rCHT}團隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.17,0:38:35.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Looks, throws, catches, hustles. Part of one big team.\N{\rCHT}投球 接球 打暗號構成一個球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.14,0:38:41.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bats himself the live-long day, Babe Ruth, Ty Cobb, and so on.\N{\rCHT}打拼出自己的人生 盧斯、庫伯（棒球選手）都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.15,0:38:47.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,If his team don't field...what is he?\N{\rCHT}如果球隊沒勝出 那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.44,0:38:51.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,You follow me?\N{\rCHT}你們懂我意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.49,0:38:54.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,No one.\N{\rCHT}什麼都不算
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.36,0:38:59.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sunny day, the stands are full of fans. What does he have to say?\N{\rCHT}現在天氣晴朗 看臺上全是人\N他有什麼話說
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.50,0:39:05.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going out there for myself.\N{\rCHT}我上場是為了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.33,0:39:12.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,But...I get nowhere unless the team wins.\N{\rCHT}但是除非球隊贏球我才有功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.58,0:39:49.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,'Now I lay me down to sleep'\N{\rCHT}在我睡覺的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.42,0:39:53.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,'I pray the Lord my soul to keep'\N{\rCHT}我祈天主佑我靈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.01,0:39:56.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,'lf I should die before I wake'\N{\rCHT}當我清醒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.01,0:39:59.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,'I pray the Lord my soul to take'\N{\rCHT}我祈天主護我靈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.60,0:40:01.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Amen. God bless...\N{\rCHT}阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.72,0:40:05.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,God bless Mommy, God bless Annie, God bless Daddy. Amen.\N{\rCHT}上帝保佑媽媽 保佑爸爸 保佑洋娃娃 阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.92,0:40:08.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Amen.\N{\rCHT}阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.91,0:40:21.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good night, Daddy. Good night, little girl.\N{\rCHT}晚安 爸爸 晚安 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.16,0:40:25.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Want to rub Eskimo? Butterfly?\N{\rCHT}要擦鼻子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.97,0:40:37.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are you going? What?\N{\rCHT}你上哪去?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.22,0:40:41.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?\N{\rCHT}你要到哪去?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.93,0:40:44.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go downstairs, some work to do for tomorrow.\N{\rCHT}我要下樓去準備明天的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.98,0:40:49.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,You had a full day today, though? Yes, I certainly did.\N{\rCHT}你忙了一天了 是嗎 是的 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:51.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you've still got some energy left?\N{\rCHT}你還有剩餘精力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.80,0:40:53.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, a lot of work.\N{\rCHT}工作真多
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.69,0:40:59.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you come up and brush my hair? You 'Detective'\N{\rCHT}你何不上來替我梳梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.44,0:41:09.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,“緝酒戰士終於得勝”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.13,0:41:17.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,How are we doing Capone's organisation is diverse.\N{\rCHT}進展如何 卡彭的組織真是複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:21.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,It owns Canadian Holding Company Associations, which owns in turn\N{\rCHT}你看 他們有加拿大控股公司
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.76,0:41:25.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Green Light Laundry, Midwest Cabs, Jolly Time Playthings...\N{\rCHT}旗下又有洗衣店、車廠、玩具公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.89,0:41:28.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jolly Time Playthings? Yes.\N{\rCHT}玩具公司? 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.73,0:41:31.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remind me to get a present for my daughter.\N{\rCHT}記得提醒我買玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.52,0:41:35.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,...Bahama Ship-to-Shore, Miss Lucy Togs...the list is endless!\N{\rCHT}巴拿馬船運公司 說也說不完
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:39.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,And all the business is legitimate, and none is owned by Al Capone.\N{\rCHT}全都在他人名下 沒有一家是登記于卡彭名下的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.28,0:41:42.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,But we can get him on income tax evasion if we can show\N{\rCHT}我們無法因他未報稅而告他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.49,0:41:46.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,that any of the 'organisation' business money is going to him.\N{\rCHT}除非我們能證明 這些公司的錢都流向他那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.83,0:41:51.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Legally, he receives no income. He doesn't receive anything?\N{\rCHT}在法律上 他沒得利益 他沒有任何收入?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.25,0:41:54.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness? You have a visitor. Mister Ness!\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 有訪客 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.00,0:41:58.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Could we talk for a minute? I'm John O'Shea, Alderman...\N{\rCHT}我能和你談談嗎? 地檢處的奧立佛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.30,0:42:00.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know who you are.\N{\rCHT}我知道你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.10,0:42:06.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you excuse us?\N{\rCHT}請你們出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.81,0:42:11.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,We are busy with several large operations. What can I do for you?\N{\rCHT}我們的工作正忙 請問有何貴幹?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.94,0:42:15.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I came up to congratulate you on a job well done.\N{\rCHT}我是來恭賀你們完成了件大功
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.82,0:42:21.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Share your good fortune on such a lovely day.\N{\rCHT}來分享你們的一些好運
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.91,0:42:26.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's that?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.50,0:42:34.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is that? Mr Ness, you're an educated man.\N{\rCHT}那是什麼? 奈斯先生你是個受過教育的人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.71,0:42:38.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me pay you the compliment of being blunt.\N{\rCHT}我非常敬佩你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.38,0:42:44.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,There is a large and popular business which you are causing dismay.\N{\rCHT}有一件很大很熱門的生意 受到了你們的干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.26,0:42:50.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just cross the street and let things take their course?\N{\rCHT}你何不睜隻眼閉隻眼聽其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.23,0:42:53.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you come in here, please?\N{\rCHT}你們進來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.57,0:43:02.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,In Roman times, when a fellow tried to bribe a public official,\N{\rCHT}在羅馬時代 如果有人被判行賄官員
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.61,0:43:05.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,they would cut off his nose, sew him in a bag\N{\rCHT}他會被割掉鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.03,0:43:08.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,with a wild animal, and throw that bag in the river.\N{\rCHT}和一隻野獸裝入同一袋中 再被丟入河中
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.87,0:43:13.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,You tell your master that we must agree to...disagree!\N{\rCHT}你去告訴你的主子 我們一致同意反對你們
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.71,0:43:18.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're making a mistake. I'm beginning to enjoy my mistakes.\N{\rCHT}你犯了大錯 我已經犯錯了 我正開始樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.13,0:43:22.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,You fellows are 'untouchable' is that it? No one can get to you?\N{\rCHT}你們鐵面無私 是不是 沒人能動你們?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.95,0:43:26.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You tell Capone... that I'll see him in hell.\N{\rCHT}去告訴卡彭 我會送他下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.51,0:43:31.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nice house!\N{\rCHT}嘿 好房子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.73,0:43:34.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said, nice house! Do you live there?\N{\rCHT}我說 好一座房子 你住在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.23,0:43:40.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Little girl's having a birthday, huh?\N{\rCHT}小女孩要過生日是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.07,0:43:42.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.24,0:43:44.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nice to have a family.\N{\rCHT}有個家真好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.20,0:43:50.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.\N{\rCHT}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.12,0:43:54.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,A man should take care, see that nothing happens to them.\N{\rCHT}你要好好照顧 免得出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.60,0:44:11.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Catherine? !\N{\rCHT}凱瑟林
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.06,0:44:15.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Catherine!\N{\rCHT}凱瑟林
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.14,0:44:17.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where's the baby? She's upstairs. Eliot!\N{\rCHT}孩子呢 她在樓上 艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.45,0:44:34.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,What were you doing up? I had to finish my ironing.\N{\rCHT}你在幹什麼 我在熨衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.37,0:44:39.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,You did? You're gonna come with Daddy now, okay?\N{\rCHT}是嗎 跟爸爸來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.18,0:44:53.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eliot? Okay, it's all right!\N{\rCHT}艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.81,0:44:56.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.\N{\rCHT}我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.31,0:45:00.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay there! Keep your eye on the street!\N{\rCHT}留在那裡 注意街上
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:05.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where's Malone? On the stake-out. He'll be here.\N{\rCHT}馬龍呢? 他在監視嫌疑犯 馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.61,0:45:09.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who's this guy? He's on Malone's list. He's okay.\N{\rCHT}他是誰 他是我們的人 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.45,0:45:15.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Drive to the station. She'll let you know where to go when you get there.\N{\rCHT}好吧 送他們到車站 到了後告訴我一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.23,0:45:17.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take off your hat.\N{\rCHT}是的 長官 帽子脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.66,0:45:21.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anything happens, shoot first. You understand me?\N{\rCHT}發生什麼事就先開槍 明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.21,0:45:23.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr Ness.\N{\rCHT}是的 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.59,0:45:31.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eskimo and butterfly, Dad. Okay.\N{\rCHT}擦擦鼻子 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.27,0:45:37.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, go!\N{\rCHT}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.37,0:46:01.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Malone!\N{\rCHT}馬龍
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.13,0:46:03.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are they okay? Yeah.\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.79,0:46:07.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You sure the cop's okay? He'd better be, he's my cousin.\N{\rCHT}很好 那個員警沒問題吧 應該沒問題 他是我表弟
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.38,0:46:10.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to hurt the man, Malone! You hear me? !\N{\rCHT}我要抓那個人 馬龍你聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.80,0:46:13.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to take the battle to him. I want to hurt Capone.\N{\rCHT}我要開始戰鬥 我要打擊卡彭
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.97,0:46:17.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, then, a Merry Christmas, we've got some great news.\N{\rCHT}那麼聖誕快樂 因為我有個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.68,0:46:20.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,A huge international shipment's coming.\N{\rCHT}將有大批私貨運來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.35,0:46:25.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've got the time, the place and the whole shebang.\N{\rCHT}我們知道時間、地點以及整個作業
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.15,0:46:28.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, what are we doing standing here, then?\N{\rCHT}那我們還等什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.32,0:46:31.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you come by this information?\N{\rCHT}你哪裡來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.53,0:46:33.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the second rule of police work:\N{\rCHT}那是員警工作的第二課
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.87,0:46:36.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,if you want to keep a secret, don't tell the boss.\N{\rCHT}如果你想保守秘密 就別告訴頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.33,0:46:45.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know he's making over $3 million a year?\N{\rCHT}他每年黑的錢超過三百萬元
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.38,0:46:48.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,But he's paid no taxes, nothing's in his name.\N{\rCHT}但他沒交稅 因為不是以他的名義
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.17,0:46:50.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we can establish any payments to him,\N{\rCHT}如果我們能確認他收到任何一筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.63,0:46:53.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,we can prosecute him for income tax evasion.\N{\rCHT}我們就可告他逃稅
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.89,0:46:55.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\rCHT}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.43,0:46:59.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said, we can prosecute him for income tax evasion!\N{\rCHT}我說我們可告他逃稅
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.98,0:47:03.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Try a murderer for not paying his taxes? !\N{\rCHT}以逃稅罪名控告殺人兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.52,0:47:06.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better than nothing.\N{\rCHT}好過沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.77,0:47:10.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right. How do we link him to the money?\N{\rCHT}好吧 要怎麼做到
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.86,0:47:14.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\N{\rCHT}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.53,0:47:18.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep, Oscar.\N{\rCHT}去睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.75,0:48:08.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,A convoy of 5-10 trucks with good Canadian whiskey\N{\rCHT}有五到十輛卡車滿載加拿大威士卡
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.17,0:48:12.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,will be met by a high-level member of the Capone organisation.\N{\rCHT}由卡彭組織中的好手交易
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.05,0:48:15.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,He will be bringing full payment for the shipment in cash.\N{\rCHT}他攜帶現金當場交易
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.84,0:48:21.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, the meet is to take place just over the border on the American side.\N{\rCHT}交易地點在邊界 美國這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.93,0:48:25.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,We want to confiscate the liquor and the cash.\N{\rCHT}我們的目標是沒收私酒和現款
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.35,0:48:29.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain? We will await their signal.\N{\rCHT}隊長 我們會等他們的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.48,0:48:32.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,When they're on the road and have given the signal,\N{\rCHT}當他們上路後信號發出
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.82,0:48:36.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,we will engage from the Canadian side of the bridge.\N{\rCHT}我們將由加拿大那邊攻擊橋那一端
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.82,0:48:39.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thus taking them by surprise from the rear.\N{\rCHT}出其不意攻擊他們背後
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.03,0:48:43.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,And surprise, as you very well know, Mr Ness, is half the battle.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 突擊就已贏得了一半的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.91,0:48:47.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Surprise is half the battle. Many things are half the battle.\N{\rCHT}突擊只贏了一半 很多事只是一半還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.33,0:48:51.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Losing is half the battle. Let's think about what is all the battle.\N{\rCHT}還有一半機會會輸 我們要贏得全部
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:54.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's take the fight to them, gentlemen!\N{\rCHT}各位 向他們開戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.59,0:48:57.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.59,0:49:01.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right! Move out!\N{\rCHT}好 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.07,0:49:22.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.\N{\rCHT}別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.58,0:49:26.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it easy! lt'll all happen in time.\N{\rCHT}別緊張 船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.75,0:49:30.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the job.\N{\rCHT}這就是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.33,0:49:34.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't wait for it to happen, don't even want it to happen.\N{\rCHT}別期待它發生 不希望它發生
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.21,0:49:37.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just watch what does happen.\N{\rCHT}只是等著看發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.05,0:49:40.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you my 'tutor'?\N{\rCHT}你是我的導師?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.30,0:49:44.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, that I am.\N{\rCHT}是的 我是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.98,0:49:50.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you check it already? Yes, I did.\N{\rCHT}你檢查過了嗎 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.02,0:49:52.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then leave it alone.\N{\rCHT}那就別再碰了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.77,0:49:55.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a good cop, Giuseppe.\N{\rCHT}你是個好員警
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.57,0:49:59.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're doing good. You're gonna do just fine.\N{\rCHT}你很不錯 你會幹得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.62,0:50:05.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wallace, are you cold? Yes, I am, a little.\N{\rCHT}華萊士你冷嗎 有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.91,0:50:09.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then stamp your feet. It'll keep you warm.\N{\rCHT}不斷的跺腳 會使你暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.21,0:50:12.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,You learn something, 20 years walking the beat.\N{\rCHT}那是我20年巡夜的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.50,0:50:17.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stitches and standing in the rain...\N{\rCHT}站在風雪、大雨中學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.03,0:50:48.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mr Ness...\N{\rCHT}聽我說 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.12,0:50:51.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I had an idea.\N{\rCHT}我有個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.22,0:51:50.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,You all have your spare shells?\N{\rCHT}你們都帶好彈藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.74,0:52:09.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you have to fire, hold low and squeeze.\N{\rCHT}如果要開槍的話 臥倒 不要留情
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.56,0:52:12.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,And put your man down.\N{\rCHT}把對手幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.96,0:52:17.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because he'll do the same to you.\N{\rCHT}因為他們也想要你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.83,0:52:20.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shoot to kill.\N{\rCHT}槍槍致命
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.30,0:52:24.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what I said? Yes, I did. Shoot to kill.\N{\rCHT}聽到了嗎 是的 聽到了 槍槍致命
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.22,0:52:28.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go.\N{\rCHT}出發
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.16,0:52:53.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Easy...\N{\rCHT}放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.75,0:52:57.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Canadians will not show until I flash the badge.\N{\rCHT}加拿大人在我發出信號前不會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.58,0:53:01.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we must cover the ground to the bridge as quickly as possible.\N{\rCHT}所以我們要儘快沖到橋上
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.38,0:53:03.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,George, the count's right.\N{\rCHT}喬治 看來沒錯 數目正確
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.30,0:53:06.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about the size of these barrels!\N{\rCHT}我擔心的不是數目我擔心的是酒桶的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.80,0:53:09.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Malone, you and I will take the men...\N{\rCHT}馬龍 我們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.68,0:53:12.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move it! Move it, Georgie!\N{\rCHT}加拿大騎警…喬治
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.81,0:53:16.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get over here! Leave the stuff in the cars!\N{\rCHT}快走 把貨留下!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.27,0:53:18.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Charge!\N{\rCHT}沖啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.81,0:53:22.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell! You got to die of something\N{\rCHT}管他的 人總免不了一死
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.03,0:53:30.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look! Here they come! Mounties! Let's get out of here!\N{\rCHT}他們來了…離開這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.20,0:53:32.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move, move!\N{\rCHT}快 快!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.34,0:53:49.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!\N{\rCHT}真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.89,0:53:53.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here are the codes. Give me that.\N{\rCHT}帳本 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.14,0:53:55.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't let those cars off the bridge!\N{\rCHT}別讓車子下橋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.78,0:54:15.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone, take the first car!\N{\rCHT}斯通 攔住第一輛車 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.37,0:54:20.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get this shit out of the way!\N{\rCHT}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.48,0:54:41.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tough guy!\N{\rCHT}混球!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.19,0:54:46.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone!\N{\rCHT}斯通
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.15,0:54:51.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone!\N{\rCHT}斯通
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.16,0:54:53.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.\N{\rCHT}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.03,0:54:57.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,You thugs!\N{\rCHT}兇手們!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.26,0:55:13.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,You all right?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.72,0:55:16.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There he is! Go get him!\N{\rCHT}是的 他在那裡 去抓他
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.23,0:55:33.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right! Enough of this running shit!\N{\rCHT}好了 別再跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.53,0:55:37.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, Georgie-boy! Well, what have we got here?\N{\rCHT}喬治小子 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.37,0:55:40.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N{\rCHT}問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.58,0:57:04.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right! Drop the gun!\N{\rCHT}好了 把槍丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.25,0:57:06.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put your hands in the air, you're under arrest.\N{\rCHT}把手舉起來 你被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.83,0:57:10.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said, drop it!\N{\rCHT}我說了 槍丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.30,0:57:21.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,God, didn't ya hear what I said? !\N{\rCHT}你沒聽見我的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.79,0:57:24.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you, deaf? !\N{\rCHT}你是聾子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.18,0:57:27.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is this, a game? !\N{\rCHT}這只是遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.92,0:57:55.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here. Sit down.\N{\rCHT}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.01,0:58:06.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone's gonna be all right.\N{\rCHT}斯通不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.93,0:58:10.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got the fellow with the satchel.\N{\rCHT}我抓到拿手提袋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.53,0:58:19.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,I had to kill him. Oh, yeah.\N{\rCHT}我不得不殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.11,0:58:22.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's as dead as Julius Caesar.\N{\rCHT}對 他死的像愷撒 (愷撒遇刺時自以為刀槍不入)
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.28,0:58:27.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you rather it was you? No, I would not.\N{\rCHT}你希望死的是你嗎 不 我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.16,0:58:31.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, then you've done your duty. Go home and sleep well tonight.\N{\rCHT}那你已經盡到責任了 今晚可回去好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.96,0:58:35.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,The things you see when you're out without your gun.\N{\rCHT}你已失去了你的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.42,0:58:39.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you're a long way from the Southside, George.\N{\rCHT}你現在離南區遠得很 喬治
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.30,0:58:43.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you. Did you come here to open a shooting gallery?\N{\rCHT}我在和你說話 你是來此開戰的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.18,0:58:46.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to write down the names of your superiors and contacts.\N{\rCHT}我要你寫出你老闆和你連絡人的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.77,0:58:49.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you kiss my ass?\N{\rCHT}你去吻我的臭屁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.98,0:58:52.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you didn't hear me. Eliot?\N{\rCHT}也許你沒聽懂 艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.40,0:58:54.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've broken the law... Eliot!\N{\rCHT}你射擊聯邦官員違反禁酒令
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.69,0:58:56.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can be tough in Leavenworth for 30 years.\N{\rCHT}你可能會被關上三十年
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.94,0:59:00.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're going inside for all day! Is that what you want?\N{\rCHT}你可以在裡面待上一輩子 你喜歡那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.20,0:59:03.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eliot! What? !\N{\rCHT}什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.16,0:59:05.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at this!\N{\rCHT}看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.74,0:59:08.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at this! What is this?\N{\rCHT}你看 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.79,0:59:12.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is this?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.38,0:59:17.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a lot of money changing hands in this book.\N{\rCHT}你這帳本上有許多錢轉出
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.38,0:59:21.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is this, 'war'? And 'police precincts'\N{\rCHT}這是什麼意思 “戰爭”“員警分局”?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.30,0:59:26.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you got a heading here... 'Circuit Court'\N{\rCHT}還有這個“巡迴法庭”是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.85,0:59:30.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a heading here, 'Circuit Court' What is this?\N{\rCHT}“巡迴法庭”是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.73,0:59:33.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing There's nothing you can make out of it.\N{\rCHT}沒什麼 你不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.90,0:59:37.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,If any of these coded entries indicate payment to Capone,\N{\rCHT}如果我們能證明這些錢是付給卡彭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.44,0:59:39.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,then we can put Capone away.\N{\rCHT}我們就能將卡彭繩之以法
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.44,0:59:43.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Which entry is Al Capone? A. Costa, is that his code name?\N{\rCHT}告訴我們 哪一些錢是付給卡彭的? A是卡彭的代號嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.39,0:59:46.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll do the whole thing in the joint unless you help us.\N{\rCHT}除非你幫助我們不然你會坐一輩子牢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.35,0:59:48.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Translate this ledger for us!\N{\rCHT}我要你將這些代號翻譯出來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.02,0:59:50.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,In hell. In hell? !\N{\rCHT}去你的 去你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.91,0:59:55.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,You will hang high unless you cooperate.\N{\rCHT}除非你合作不然你會被高高的吊死
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.71,0:59:59.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,This man can finger Al Capone, put him behind bars.\N{\rCHT}這個人可指證卡彭 使卡彭入獄
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.55,1:00:01.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys just fuck off? !\N{\rCHT}你們去死吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.84,1:00:08.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not fucking with you! We'll have that information one way or another.\N{\rCHT}我懶得跟你說了 我們總有方法問出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.35,1:00:10.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not that way. Out. You're gonna talk!\N{\rCHT}你會說的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.94,1:00:13.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be begging to talk!\N{\rCHT}你會求我讓你招供
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.48,1:00:16.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You dirty son-of-a-bitch! Enough out of you.\N{\rCHT}你這個下流胚子 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.23,1:00:22.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, you, on your feet!\N{\rCHT}起來 你 站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.74,1:00:26.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need you to help me to translate this book!\N{\rCHT}我要你替我譯這本帳簿
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.28,1:00:28.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna ask you a second time.\N{\rCHT}我不會問你第二次
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.49,1:00:30.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna count to three.\N{\rCHT}我只數到三
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.58,1:00:36.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Can't you talk with a gun in your mouth?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了? 嘴裡有支槍就說不出話了?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.21,1:00:39.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,One.\N{\rCHT}一
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.80,1:00:45.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two!\N{\rCHT}二
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.64,1:00:49.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Three.\N{\rCHT}三
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.22,1:00:51.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna talk!\N{\rCHT}好 我願意說
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.89,1:00:56.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't ! I'm gonna tell ya whatever ya want. What do ya want to know?\N{\rCHT}不 我什麼都招 你們要知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.61,1:01:03.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, don't let him clean himself until after he talks.\N{\rCHT}他說完後 才讓他清潔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.57,1:01:06.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, ask him what you want to know.\N{\rCHT}現在想知道什麼就問他吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.82,1:01:11.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right... Okay, I want to know the name of the bookkeeper.\N{\rCHT}好了 我要知道記帳員的姓名
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.20,1:01:15.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want a complete translation of the code. I want a complete...\N{\rCHT}我要你將代號全譯出來 我要完全的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.54,1:01:18.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mister Ness!\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.13,1:01:26.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,I do not approve of your methods!\N{\rCHT}我不贊成你的做法
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.59,1:01:32.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, you're not from Chicago.\N{\rCHT}是嗎? 你不是從芝加哥來的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.48,1:01:38.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? They got the shipment.\N{\rCHT}什麼? 他們把貨沒收了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.98,1:01:41.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? ! They got the whole shipment.\N{\rCHT}什麼? 他們把所有的貨都沒收了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.73,1:01:45.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want that son-of-a-bitch dead! We're trying to locate...\N{\rCHT}我要那個混蛋沒命 我要他死
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.90,1:01:51.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,What am I, alone in this world? Did I ask you what you're trying to do?\N{\rCHT}搞什麼? 我問過你打算做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.03,1:01:56.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to get this fuck where he breathes! I want Eliot Ness dead!\N{\rCHT}我要你除掉他的人 我要你找出他的住處 我要他死
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.83,1:02:00.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want his family dead, his house burnt to the ground!\N{\rCHT}我要他全家死光 我要在他的骨灰上撒尿
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.25,1:02:02.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to piss on his ashes!\N{\rCHT}我要他知道厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.75,1:02:08.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at this guy, this guy, he's so serious.\N{\rCHT}看看他 這小傢伙 他好嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.22,1:02:11.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, he's got a lot on his mind. He does?\N{\rCHT}他腦子裡在想很多事 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.68,1:02:13.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. Like what?\N{\rCHT}是的 像什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.18,1:02:17.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like what his name is.\N{\rCHT}想他叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.06,1:02:21.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,John, I thought that was all settled. I thought we liked John.\N{\rCHT}約翰 不是說好了嗎? 約翰 我們都喜歡這名字
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.44,1:02:24.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I suppose his middle name will be Law.\N{\rCHT}奈斯 他該叫朗恩
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.69,1:02:28.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,No...it'll be Edgar.\N{\rCHT}不 叫艾得格
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.53,1:02:33.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,It'll be J. Edgar... I don't think so.\N{\rCHT}叫J.艾得格 我覺得不好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.70,1:02:39.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,God, you're beautiful.\N{\rCHT}老天 你真美
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.92,1:02:43.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should have seen us last night.\N{\rCHT}你昨晚來看我們會更美
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.21,1:02:48.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know. I should have been here. I wanted to be here.\N{\rCHT}我知道 我該來 我想來
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.59,1:02:52.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know. I understand, I do.\N{\rCHT}我知道 我瞭解 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.39,1:02:56.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just tell me, are you being careful?\N{\rCHT}只要你小心就好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.47,1:03:00.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Careful as mice. Are you making progress?\N{\rCHT}我小心得像老鼠一樣 有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.19,1:03:02.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Progress? Yes?\N{\rCHT}進展?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.56,1:03:06.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mrs Ness, I think your husband just became the man who got Al Capone.\N{\rCHT}奈斯太太 我想你先生逮到卡彭了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.37,1:03:20.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen! A subpoena was issued for Alphonse Capone\N{\rCHT}先生們 今天上午地檢處
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.08,1:03:25.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,by my office this morning, for the crime of evading\N{\rCHT}控告卡彭先生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.21,1:03:28.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,and conspiring to evade Federal Income Tax.\N{\rCHT}罪名是漏稅及圖謀逃稅
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.96,1:03:32.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's the maximum he could get? If convicted on all counts,\N{\rCHT}卡彭先生會判刑多久? 如果所有罪名成立
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.30,1:03:36.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Capone could have up to 28 years.\N{\rCHT}卡彭可判二十八年
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.60,1:03:39.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, that's all. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}失陪了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.31,1:03:50.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,The car's in the yard. When ya get him there, don't answer the phone.\N{\rCHT}車子在巷子裡 到了之後 別接電話
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.82,1:03:53.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll call, let it ring... Twice.\N{\rCHT}我們來時 讓鈴聲… 響二次
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.16,1:03:55.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll call... From the corner.\N{\rCHT}我們會打電話… 在拐角處
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.28,1:03:59.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anybody knocks on the door... Come out shooting. I got it.\N{\rCHT}有人敲門的話就… 開槍射擊 我都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.08,1:04:02.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,You enjoy the tactical aspects of law enforcement, Oscar?\N{\rCHT}看來你很喜歡執法的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.29,1:04:05.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Much more diverting than accounting.\N{\rCHT}是 比當會計有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.29,1:04:07.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm being good to you, you got to be good to me.\N{\rCHT}我對你們好 你們也要回報我
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.67,1:04:11.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,We made a deal, we're gonna stick to it, okay?\N{\rCHT}我們有協議 我們會遵守的 好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.55,1:04:19.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, much more diverting than accounting.\N{\rCHT}對的 比當會計有意思多了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.77,1:04:22.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, we see yous tonight.\N{\rCHT}好 晚上見
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.23,1:04:26.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, all the way down and no stops.\N{\rCHT}好了 一直下去中間不停
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.03,1:04:37.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,...he's been saying, "I will speak up."\N{\rCHT}他能說:我會大聲地說
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.53,1:04:43.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,For which I must commend the excellent work\N{\rCHT}我得讚揚艾略特.奈斯
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.87,1:04:47.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,of Eliot Ness and his squad of Untouchables.\N{\rCHT}和他隊伍的出色表現
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.13,1:04:53.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,What was it, a boy or a girl? Boy.\N{\rCHT}恭喜 是男孩還是女孩? 男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.04,1:04:55.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! What's his name? John.\N{\rCHT}恭喜 叫什麼名字 約翰
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.91,1:04:59.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,John? Yeah. John James.\N{\rCHT}約翰 是的 約翰.詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.06,1:05:02.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,So she's okay? Yeah, she's okay.\N{\rCHT}她好吧 她很好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.64,1:05:06.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,In fact, when she gets out, she wants to repaint the house.\N{\rCHT}她說她出院後要油漆房子
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.31,1:05:10.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then she'll find the house too small, you'll have to move.\N{\rCHT}再下來她會嫌房子小你就必須搬家
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.86,1:05:16.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goodness, it's nice to be married. If you can stand the pain.\N{\rCHT}結婚真不錯 如果你能忍受痛苦的話
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.36,1:05:18.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Burns, where's Mr Wallace?\N{\rCHT}伯恩先生 華萊士呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.16,1:05:23.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see him? He just went down in the service elevator.\N{\rCHT}你見到他們嗎? 他剛從貨物電梯下去
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.66,1:05:28.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You keep an eye out at all times... Take it easy, we'll be fine.\N{\rCHT}必須隨時警戒 我瞭解他們 別緊張
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.51,1:05:42.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did he say the service elevator? Yes.\N{\rCHT}他是說搭貨物電梯? 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.90,1:05:52.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wallace! Wallace! Here, let's take the stairs.\N{\rCHT}華萊士華萊士走樓梯
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.69,1:06:38.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, no! Easy... Easy!\N{\rCHT}不 別衝動 別衝動
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.32,1:06:43.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oscar.\N{\rCHT}“動搖”
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.82,1:07:24.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jesus.\N{\rCHT}天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.79,1:07:30.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,You gonna be all right?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.68,1:07:56.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's always a crime when a young guy goes down in the line, Jimmy.\N{\rCHT}看到自己人躺在那裡 心裡實在很難過
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.94,1:08:00.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to see it happen to someone I know.\N{\rCHT}我恨見到這事發生在我認識的人身上
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.28,1:08:04.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's better not to get involved.\N{\rCHT}有時候 置身事外最明智
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.11,1:08:10.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jimmy! Take a day off. Get out of the city for a while.\N{\rCHT}吉米 請一天假離開市區
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.33,1:08:12.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?\N{\rCHT}懂我意思吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.47,1:08:31.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Al Capone. We have no Mr Capone...\N{\rCHT}艾爾卡彭 我們這裡沒有卡彭先生
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.60,1:08:35.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know, get him. We have no Mr Capone...\N{\rCHT}叫他 叫他 我們這裡沒有卡彭先生
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.56,1:08:37.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said...\N{\rCHT}我說了…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.82,1:08:47.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Something you want here? My friend was killed today.\N{\rCHT}你有事嗎 我的朋友今天被殺了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.35,1:08:50.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't care. You don't care.\N{\rCHT}幹我屁事 不幹你的事?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.00,1:08:55.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now he does.\N{\rCHT}現在有關了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.50,1:09:00.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on here, Capone. You want to fight? You and me, right here?\N{\rCHT}來吧 卡彭 你要打嗎 你要打嗎? 你和我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.05,1:09:01.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's it, come on!\N{\rCHT}怎麼了 來呀
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.59,1:09:05.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,You afraid to come out from behind your men, to stand up for yourself?\N{\rCHT}別躲在爪牙背後不敢自己站出來?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.38,1:09:09.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want to do the mat now? Yeah! Come on, you son-of-a-bitch!\N{\rCHT}你想現在幹是不是 你要現在來嗎? 來呀 你這狗娘養的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.60,1:09:11.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? Easy.\N{\rCHT}什麼? 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.68,1:09:15.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,You talk to me like that in front of my son? Fuck you and your family!\N{\rCHT}你在我手下面前那樣罵我 幹他媽的你和你家人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.98,1:09:21.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Easy. It's me. It's me!\N{\rCHT}是我 是我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.40,1:09:23.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not this way.\N{\rCHT}這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.32,1:09:26.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,You fuck, you got nothing You're nothing but talk and a badge.\N{\rCHT}你什麼都沒有 我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.20,1:09:32.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're here because you got nothing in court, no bookkeeper, nothing\N{\rCHT}你來此是因為你沒有證據 你沒有證物 沒有簿記員
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.12,1:09:36.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you were a man, you would've done it now! You got nothing you punk!\N{\rCHT}你要是男子漢的話就現在來幹 你一無所有 混球
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.92,1:09:49.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, no, I understand.\N{\rCHT}不 我…我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.18,1:09:52.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I understand.\N{\rCHT}相信我 我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.48,1:10:02.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, what's happened?\N{\rCHT}怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.32,1:10:08.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,He says he can't be unprotected.\N{\rCHT}他說他不能沒有證據
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.70,1:10:12.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is it that the guy says?\N{\rCHT}他究竟怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.58,1:10:15.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,He says he won't make a fool out of himself,\N{\rCHT}他說他不願意讓自己出醜
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.41,1:10:18.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,and he won't go into court without a witness.\N{\rCHT}沒有證人 所以他要撤回他的控訴
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.96,1:10:23.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,So tomorrow morning the D.A. will announce that he's dropping the case.\N{\rCHT}所以，明天早上，D.A.將宣佈他的案子情況
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.42,1:10:27.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's gonna give up. He won't do it without a witness.\N{\rCHT}他要放棄 沒有證人他不願開庭
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.51,1:10:30.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have Wallace's files and the ledgers.\N{\rCHT}我們有華萊士的檔案和那帳本
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.39,1:10:34.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a time when I think you have to cut your losses.\N{\rCHT}有時候你得承認失敗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.14,1:10:37.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello?\N{\rCHT}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.23,1:10:41.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N{\rCHT}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.86,1:10:45.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.20,1:10:51.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't have a family.\N{\rCHT}他沒有家人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.58,1:10:56.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,How is everything there?\N{\rCHT}情形如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.54,1:11:03.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, you do it however you want.\N{\rCHT}不 你看著辦就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.09,1:11:07.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I promise I will.\N{\rCHT}我保證我會的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.42,1:11:10.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You give her my love.\N{\rCHT}代我問候他
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.97,1:11:13.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you, too.\N{\rCHT}我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.14,1:11:20.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness, we got a ledger here listing payments to Chicago City officials.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 這本帳本有費用支出牽涉芝加哥政府官員
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.52,1:11:24.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,We got Al Capone, Frank Nitti... I think that's enough for today.\N{\rCHT}也有卡彭那批人…今天到此為止 明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.69,1:11:28.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we don't stay on top... That'll do. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}斯通 就這樣了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.97,1:11:33.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd like to request to stick around.\N{\rCHT}我要求留下來
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.03,1:11:36.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,We got to bust these guys. I know we got to.\N{\rCHT}我們要逮住那些人 我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.50,1:11:47.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that it?\N{\rCHT}就此結束了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.67,1:11:51.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry? You heard me.\N{\rCHT}你說什麼? 你聽見我的話了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.51,1:11:54.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,My question is, are we done?\N{\rCHT}我在問 我們就此結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.97,1:11:58.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think we're done.\N{\rCHT}是的 我想是的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.56,1:12:01.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we sat in at a game that was above our head?\N{\rCHT}你是說我們是輸的一方
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.64,1:12:04.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,It appears so. It appears so to Mr Wallace.\N{\rCHT}似乎是如此 對華萊士來說的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.23,1:12:06.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's dead! And the D.A. is gonna drop the case!\N{\rCHT}他死了 檢察官要撤銷案子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.73,1:12:09.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,He will not go into court without a witness\N{\rCHT}沒有證人他不願起訴
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.23,1:12:12.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,and without Capone's bookkeeper, Walter Payne.\N{\rCHT}沒有卡彭的簿記員他不願起訴的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.40,1:12:17.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you prepared to do now? What would you have me do?\N{\rCHT}那你現在打算怎麼辦 你希望我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.45,1:12:20.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have taken this as far as it can go.\N{\rCHT}我已盡力了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.22,1:12:38.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,What did your wife want? She wanted to know if I was...\N{\rCHT}你太太要幹什麼? 她要知道我是否…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.39,1:12:42.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,My wife? Yeah.\N{\rCHT}我太太? 對
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.15,1:12:49.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,She wanted to know if I was all right.\N{\rCHT}她想知道事情是否順利
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.36,1:12:53.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's nice being married, eh?\N{\rCHT}結婚真不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.95,1:12:56.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.49,1:12:59.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's sitting in some room surrounded by people she doesn't know,\N{\rCHT}她在那裡由一群陌生人保護著
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.02,1:13:04.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,going over... kitchen colour charts or something.\N{\rCHT}只能在想廚房該漆什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.92,1:13:16.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Some part of the world still cares what colour the kitchen is.\N{\rCHT}誰在乎廚房該漆什麼色
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.18,1:13:25.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eliot, I want you to do one more thing for me.\N{\rCHT}艾略特 我要你再為我做一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.90,1:13:31.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get back to the D.A. and stall him.\N{\rCHT}去檢察官那裡拖延這案子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.15,1:13:36.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, stall him with what? Just do as I say.\N{\rCHT}等一下 怎麼個拖延 照我的話去做就是了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.74,1:13:41.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I know how to find this guy.\N{\rCHT}我知道怎麼找出那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.94,1:13:43.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,“卡彭簿記員被傳喚”
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.25,1:13:47.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Walter?\N{\rCHT}沃爾特
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.21,1:13:52.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Al says we got to get out of town until he can fix this subpoena thing.\N{\rCHT}艾爾說要我們到外地去避避風頭
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.42,1:13:55.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're leaving tonight.\N{\rCHT}我們今晚動身
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.18,1:14:00.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two ball, down.\N{\rCHT}兩球入袋
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.10,1:14:07.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mike, you got a minute?\N{\rCHT}邁克 你有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.98,1:14:10.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I do now, don't I?\N{\rCHT}現在有了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.77,1:14:15.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing in a club for cops, Jimmy?\N{\rCHT}你到員警俱樂部幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.03,1:14:18.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a place for cops.\N{\rCHT}這裡只有員警能來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.82,1:14:21.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can we step outside?\N{\rCHT}到外面去談如何
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.62,1:14:26.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, but I got nothing to say to ya.\N{\rCHT}好…但我和你無話可說
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.25,1:14:35.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are we going, for a swim? Get out of the rain, you fool.\N{\rCHT}你要去哪裡? 游泳嗎 外面在下雨 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.05,1:14:41.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? What? !\N{\rCHT}什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.01,1:14:44.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just need one more piece of information.\N{\rCHT}我想再要一件情報
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.31,1:14:46.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,One more? Jimmy!\N{\rCHT}再一件 吉米
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.48,1:14:51.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just risked my life for ya. I need to find that bookkeeper.\N{\rCHT}我已為你冒了生命危險 我需要找出那個簿記員
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.65,1:14:58.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy? Y ou're crazy. I warned you to get out of town.\N{\rCHT}你瘋了! 你是瘋了 我曾警告你要離開
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.82,1:15:03.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,If they knew it was me, I'm dead. I need to find that bookkeeper.\N{\rCHT}如果他們知道是我的話我就死定了 我必須找到那簿記員
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.03,1:15:07.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're fucking nuts, man! You're out of your fucking mind!\N{\rCHT}你簡直就瘋了 你瘋了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.83,1:15:10.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I tried to save your life.\N{\rCHT}我還想救你的命
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.96,1:15:15.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off. You owe me, Jimmy, I don't owe you nothing\N{\rCHT}把手拿開 你欠我 吉米 我可什麼也不欠你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.78,1:15:19.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,My people are being killed. We're your people!\N{\rCHT}我的人被殺了 你的人 我們才是同志
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.13,1:15:24.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,You? ! You fucking run with the dagos! They've ruined this town.\N{\rCHT}你是我的同志? 是的 你和他們同流合污使得這城市敗壞
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.35,1:15:28.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,For ten years I can't say that I'm a cop for the shit that's going on!\N{\rCHT}十年來 我無法抬頭挺胸以當員警為傲
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.77,1:15:34.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ah, bullshit! Fucking bullshit! Look at yourself! Look at yourself!\N{\rCHT}狗屎 一派胡言 看看你 看看你自己
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.19,1:15:41.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go on and live the charade, with your soft clothes and federal stooges.\N{\rCHT}去做你的英雄夢吧 穿著便衣和聯邦專員辦案
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.99,1:15:46.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think he's gonna do? Keep your mouth off that!\N{\rCHT}你想他還能怎麼辦 他是想清理這城市
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.20,1:15:50.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need to know where this guy is, and I need to know now!\N{\rCHT}我要知道那簿記員在哪裡 我現在就要知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.54,1:15:54.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna rat you out for all the shit that I know that you've done!\N{\rCHT}否則我要把你這輩子 幹的醜事全揭出來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.79,1:15:57.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna turn you over!\N{\rCHT}我要告發你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.55,1:16:01.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a dead man talking to me. Is it?\N{\rCHT}你不想活了 是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.26,1:16:05.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're dead.\N{\rCHT}你死定了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.66,1:16:29.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who the hell do ya think ya are?\N{\rCHT}你以為你是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.58,1:16:32.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll have your ass hanging from the flagpole in the morning\N{\rCHT}我現在就宰掉你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.96,1:16:44.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's cut the woofing, pal. You tell me,\N{\rCHT}少說狠話了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.26,1:16:47.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,or you're going to hospital or the fucking morgue!\N{\rCHT}你想進醫院還是墳場
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.51,1:16:50.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fight it out and we'll have a case.\N{\rCHT}要怎麼拖延? 我根本無法成立此案
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.22,1:16:54.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes? On what basis? I'm not gonna make a fool...\N{\rCHT}有何依據? 我不打算起訴 我可不想鬧笑話
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.02,1:16:56.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me about making a fool out of yourself.\N{\rCHT}別說你會鬧笑話
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.86,1:16:59.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have men out there risking more than that.\N{\rCHT}我的人正在外面冒生命危險
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.65,1:17:02.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have a lead, and we are following that lead\N{\rCHT}我們有線索 我們正循線索去追查
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.36,1:17:07.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,at risk to more than our standing. So don't you dare stop now.\N{\rCHT}你現在絕不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.37,1:17:11.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Stone. Give me Ness.\N{\rCHT}是的 斯通 奈斯呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.66,1:17:13.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's at the D.A. 's.\N{\rCHT}他在檢察官的辦公室
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.46,1:17:16.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell him I know where Payne is and to meet me at my place.\N{\rCHT}告訴他我知道佩恩下落 叫他馬上到我這裡來
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.85,1:17:37.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Al! Al! Mr Capone!\N{\rCHT}艾爾.卡彭先生
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.60,1:17:42.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,What about that court case? I'm gonna tell ya something\N{\rCHT}出庭的事如何 我告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.26,1:17:46.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somebody messes with me, I'm gonna mess with him.\N{\rCHT}誰和我搗蛋我就要他好看
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.45,1:17:50.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somebody steals from me, I'm gonna say 'you stole'\N{\rCHT}有人偷我東西 我就罵他是小偷
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.83,1:17:54.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,not talk to him for spitting on the sidewalk.\N{\rCHT}我不會理會這種人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.29,1:17:55.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You understand?\N{\rCHT}你們明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.54,1:18:01.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I have done nothing to hurt these people.\N{\rCHT}我沒有傷害那些人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.25,1:18:04.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,But they're angered at me. So what do they do?\N{\rCHT}但他們生我的氣 所以他們如何做?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.21,1:18:10.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor up some income tax, for which they got no case, to annoy me.\N{\rCHT}他們便扯出交稅問題 他們根本沒證據 好使我惱怒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.89,1:18:13.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,To speak to me like men? No.\N{\rCHT}他們像男子漢嗎? 不是
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.90,1:18:16.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,To harass a peaceful man.\N{\rCHT}竟要逮捕一位講和平的人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.06,1:18:20.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I pray to God that if I ever have a grievance,\N{\rCHT}我向上帝祈禱 可以的話
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.34,1:18:23.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I would have just a little more self respect.\N{\rCHT}我只要求些自尊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.03,1:18:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you one more thing. In an all-out prize fight,\N{\rCHT}我再告訴你們一件事 一場戰鬥要等到戰鬥結束後
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.45,1:18:33.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,when one guy's left standing, that's how you know who won.\N{\rCHT}只剩一個人站著 那時才知道誰是贏家
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.94,1:18:45.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,“拉辛路”
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.92,1:18:55.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,“拉辛路 1634號”
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.04,1:21:23.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just like a wop?\N{\rCHT}真是不知好歹
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.87,1:21:27.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Brings a knife to a gun fight.\N{\rCHT}用刀來對付槍
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.51,1:21:34.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, ya dago bastard!\N{\rCHT}滾出去 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.43,1:21:37.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go on, get your ass out of here!\N{\rCHT}快點 快滾
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.78,1:23:21.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shots! Shots! I heard shots!\N{\rCHT}槍聲 我聽到槍聲
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.74,1:23:25.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay back, everybody stay back, right now.\N{\rCHT}退後 大家退後 快
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.58,1:23:27.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Round the back.\N{\rCHT}繞到後面
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.55,1:23:38.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Malone!\N{\rCHT}馬龍
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.64,1:23:43.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Malone.\N{\rCHT}馬龍
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.25,1:24:14.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goddamn! Stone!\N{\rCHT}天 斯通…斯通
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.80,1:24:19.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone!\N{\rCHT}斯通
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.22,1:24:22.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,The phone!\N{\rCHT}電話
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.39,1:24:27.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God. Call an ambulance!\N{\rCHT}叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.10,1:24:33.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is Stone, Treasury Department, 1634 Racine, we need an ambulance.\N{\rCHT}我是斯通 財政部的 派救護車至拉辛路1634號
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.94,1:24:37.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? 1634 Racine!\N{\rCHT}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.36,1:24:40.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,This? You want this?\N{\rCHT}你要這個
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.82,1:24:46.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want this?\N{\rCHT}你要這個
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.75,1:24:55.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\rCHT}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.55,1:25:04.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bookkeeper. What?\N{\rCHT}簿記員
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.84,1:25:08.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Book... The bookkeeper?\N{\rCHT}那個簿記員? 簿記員
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.10,1:25:11.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bookkeeper! The bookkeeper? What?\N{\rCHT}簿記員？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.48,1:25:15.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,The bookkeeper, he's on this train? Yes.\N{\rCHT}簿記員 他搭這班火車
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.02,1:25:17.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's on this train.\N{\rCHT}他搭這班火車?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.19,1:25:21.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now! What are you prepared to do? !\N{\rCHT}你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.37,1:25:30.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay. Stay.\N{\rCHT}撐著
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.33,1:25:32.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay! Malone...\N{\rCHT}馬龍!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.98,1:25:35.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. No, no!\N{\rCHT}不
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.79,1:25:40.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not this... Not this man...\N{\rCHT}不 不是這個
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.03,1:26:10.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Traings leaving for Miami 12.05, Mr Ness.\N{\rCHT}到邁阿密的火車十二時五分開出
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.49,1:26:14.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll be there.\N{\rCHT}我們會趕到的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.54,1:26:20.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,The bookkeeper's no good to us dead.\N{\rCHT}死的簿記員對我們沒用 斯通
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.13,1:26:22.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stone? Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}是的 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.60,1:26:26.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,“通往各班列車”
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.43,1:26:35.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cover the south entrance.\N{\rCHT}監視南邊入口
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.61,1:27:26.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're almost home. We're almost home.\N{\rCHT}我們快回到家了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.28,1:27:35.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your attention, please. The Miami Flier departs at 12.05 from 33.\N{\rCHT}往邁阿密的特快車 將於12點5分在33號月臺開出
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.45,1:27:37.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,All aboard.\N{\rCHT}乘客請儘快上車
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.80,1:27:52.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay right there. Stay right there.\N{\rCHT}你等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.01,1:27:56.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay right there. Stay right there, honey.\N{\rCHT}你等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.40,1:28:12.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your attention, please. The Miami Flier, leaving at 12.05,\N{\rCHT}往邁阿密的特快車 將於12點5分
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.53,1:28:16.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,now boarding on track 33. All aboard!\N{\rCHT}在33號月臺開出 請乘客儘快上車
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.46,1:28:33.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just here. I'm just gonna leave this right here.\N{\rCHT}就這樣停下來
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.85,1:29:28.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your attention, please. The Miami Flier, leaving at 12.05,\N{\rCHT}請注意 往邁阿密的特快車 將於12點5分
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.15,1:29:33.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,is now boarding on track 33. All aboard!\N{\rCHT}在33號月臺開出 請乘客儘快上車
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.61,1:29:36.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,One more. Here we go.\N{\rCHT}再來一次
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.47,1:30:00.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here we go. You ready?\N{\rCHT}來了 準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.18,1:30:05.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, honey. Here we go.\N{\rCHT}我在這裡 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.69,1:30:10.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your attention, please. May I have your attention, please?\N{\rCHT}請各位乘客注意
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.69,1:30:13.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the final call for the Miami Flier,\N{\rCHT}往邁阿密的特快車最後召集
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.49,1:30:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,leaving at 12.05 on track 33. All aboard!\N{\rCHT}將於12點5分在33號月臺開出 請乘客儘快上車
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.07,1:31:02.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here, let me. Get your bags. Oh, thank you so much. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}我來幫你 真多謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.74,1:31:06.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.00,1:31:11.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're such a gentleman. It's so kind of you to help me.\N{\rCHT}你真好心 肯幫助我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.04,1:31:15.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,I really wasn't sure if we'd make it or not.\N{\rCHT}我擔心自己是否能辦到
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.72,1:31:21.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is there some problem I can help you with?\N{\rCHT}有問題嗎? 我來幫你 不用
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.85,1:31:26.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. I really can't thank you enough.\N{\rCHT}我真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.31,1:31:34.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Isn't this fun? You're being such a good boy, sweetheart.\N{\rCHT}你真可愛
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.15,1:31:43.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, this is so wonderful.Thank you, sir.\N{\rCHT}你真好 真謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.29,1:31:56.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please, let me take it from here. You've been such a great help.\N{\rCHT}我來吧 先生 謝謝你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.17,1:31:59.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. We're almost there.\N{\rCHT}謝謝 我們快到了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.43,1:32:07.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll take it from here, sir. Thank you very much for your help.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.06,1:32:12.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, sweetheart. We're almost home.\N{\rCHT}別哭 寶寶 我們快到家了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.90,1:32:18.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong? Sir?\N{\rCHT}有什麼不對嗎? 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.56,1:34:17.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on, let's get out of here.\N{\rCHT}快點! 離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.98,1:34:21.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing Shut up!\N{\rCHT}你幹什麼? 閉嘴 走
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.03,1:34:27.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing Shut the fuck up!\N{\rCHT}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.78,1:34:31.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Please...\N{\rCHT}別動
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.33,1:34:34.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,My baby! Stay there. He's all right.\N{\rCHT}我的寶寶 別動 他沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.67,1:34:38.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said hold it!\N{\rCHT}我說別動
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.84,1:34:42.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm walking out with the bookkeeper.\N{\rCHT}我要和簿記員一起走出去
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.67,1:34:45.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,The bookkeeper and me are driving away.\N{\rCHT}簿記員將和我駕車離開
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.26,1:34:53.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,See? Or else he dies.He dies, and you aingt got nothing\N{\rCHT}如果他死了 你們就什麼都沒了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.14,1:35:00.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got five seconds to make up your mind.\N{\rCHT}給你們五秒鐘決定
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.11,1:35:06.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll tell ya what ya want to know! Shut up! I'm not kidding\N{\rCHT}我告訴你們…我告訴你們所想知道的一切 閉嘴 我不是說著玩
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.32,1:35:10.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's crazy! Don't let him do this, I'll tell you what you want to know!\N{\rCHT}殺了他 我什麼都告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.95,1:35:13.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got him? Yeah, I got him.\N{\rCHT}你瞄準他了 是的 我瞄準了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.50,1:35:20.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,One! Will you stop it!\N{\rCHT}一 請你們制止他
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.09,1:35:29.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take him.\N{\rCHT}解決他
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.72,1:35:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two.\N{\rCHT}二
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.37,1:36:02.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,The two coded entries in this ledger\N{\rCHT}這帳本上的記號代表了收付物件
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.25,1:36:07.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,represent cash disbursement to all levels of city officials,\N{\rCHT}包括了各級政府官員、員警人員
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.13,1:36:13.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,members of the police and to Alphonse Capone.\N{\rCHT}還有艾爾卡彭 是不是
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.76,1:36:17.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's correct. Excuse me?\N{\rCHT}沒錯 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.18,1:36:21.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said that is correct.\N{\rCHT}你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.69,1:36:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you will decipher these coded entries for us?\N{\rCHT}而你會替我們譯出帳本上的代號
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.69,1:36:31.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I will.\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.03,1:36:33.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr Payne, I can't hear you.\N{\rCHT}對不起 佩恩先生 我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.60,1:36:36.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said, I will.\N{\rCHT}是的 我會
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.58,1:36:41.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,You were in charge of disbursements for Mr Capone?\N{\rCHT}你負責替卡彭先生管帳
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.50,1:36:43.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was.\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.04,1:36:54.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you personally distributed monies vast, undeclared monies to Mr Capone?\N{\rCHT}而你是親自將那些 未報稅的鉅款交給卡彭先生
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.12,1:36:56.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.68,1:36:59.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you tell us the amounts?\N{\rCHT}你能告訴我們總數嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.93,1:37:07.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,In a three-year period I personally disbursed monies to Mr Capone\N{\rCHT}三年來 我親自交給卡彭先生
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.32,1:37:12.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,in excess of one and a third million dollars.\N{\rCHT}一百三十多萬元
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.99,1:37:18.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you repeat that amount, please?\N{\rCHT}請你再重複一次
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.95,1:37:24.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,One and a third million dollars. Thank you very much.\N{\rCHT}一百三十萬美元 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.14,1:37:43.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it. What does Capone have?\N{\rCHT}我不明白 卡彭為何有恃無恐
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.56,1:37:47.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're nailing the lid on his coffin, and he's smiling.\N{\rCHT}他一直在微笑
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.80,1:38:14.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,The son-of-a-bitch is wearing a gun in court.\N{\rCHT}那傢伙在法庭上帶槍
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.01,1:38:19.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get me the bailiff.\N{\rCHT}叫法警來
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.35,1:38:22.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,It'll be a fast trial.\N{\rCHT}很快會結束的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.52,1:38:31.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,The man in the front row wearing a white suit is carrying a gun.\N{\rCHT}那個穿白西裝的人身上帶了把槍
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.15,1:38:36.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't want this to turn into something. I'll lead you out.\N{\rCHT}我不希望在此鬧事 你叫他出去
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.95,1:38:46.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Could we speak to you a minute, please?\N{\rCHT}請你出來一下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.15,1:39:19.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get up against it. You heard him. Now, up against it!\N{\rCHT}面對牆壁 你以為你是誰? 你聽到他的話了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.20,1:39:24.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's this? Empty all your pockets, all of it.\N{\rCHT}好了 把口袋掏空放在這裡 全拿出來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.16,1:39:27.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got a permit for that. Fine, let's see it.\N{\rCHT}我有帶槍的許可 我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.08,1:39:35.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one under indictment. Everything on the table.\N{\rCHT}遭起訴的人不是我 把東西放在桌上
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.34,1:39:40.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me see. Give him his gun back.\N{\rCHT}把槍還他
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.76,1:39:43.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,"To Whom It May Concern. Please extend to the bearer, "\N{\rCHT}請給予弗蘭克尼蒂先生一切的方便和工作
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.22,1:39:47.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Mr Frank Nitti, all possible courtesy and consideration."\N{\rCHT}主席弗蘭克運往尼提，所有可能的禮遇和照顧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.31,1:39:49.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,"W illiam Thompson, Mayor of the City of Chicago."\N{\rCHT}威廉湯姆森 芝加哥市長
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.94,1:39:53.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr Ness, you'll have to give it back.\N{\rCHT}對不起 奈斯先生 你必須把槍還他
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.61,1:39:57.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fine. But that man does not go back into that courtroom.\N{\rCHT}好吧 但那傢伙不准再進入法庭
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.78,1:40:01.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me? Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}你明白嗎 是的 長官
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.12,1:40:28.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,“拉辛路1634號”
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.10,1:40:36.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,1634 Racine... You know, I used to have a friend who lived there.\N{\rCHT}拉辛路1634號 我曾有位朋友住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.54,1:40:53.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't. Let him go.\N{\rCHT}不要 讓他走
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.80,1:41:00.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,No! Here, take it.\N{\rCHT}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.30,1:45:15.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here I am, Treasury Man. Come on! Harass me!\N{\rCHT}我在這裡 財政官員 來呀 逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.14,1:45:19.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?\N{\rCHT}你在等什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.48,1:45:23.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Harass me!\N{\rCHT}別光站在那裡 逮捕我呀
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.48,1:45:30.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't push me.\N{\rCHT}別惹火了我
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.61,1:45:35.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're gonna burn you, buddy. Yeah?\N{\rCHT}我要送你下地獄 老兄 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.53,1:45:38.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm gonna come see you burn, you son-of-a-bitch!\N{\rCHT}沒錯 我要看你下獄
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.87,1:45:41.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,'Cause you killed my friend!\N{\rCHT}因為你殺了我朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.25,1:45:45.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,He died like a pig. What did you say?\N{\rCHT}他死得像只豬一樣 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.08,1:45:48.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said that your friend died screaming like a stuck Irish pig.\N{\rCHT}我說你朋友死前哀號得像豬一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.92,1:45:52.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you think about that when I beat the rap.\N{\rCHT}等我脫罪時 你慢慢想吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.90,1:46:08.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did he sound anything like that?\N{\rCHT}像你這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.01,1:46:42.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,One picture, come on, one picture.\N{\rCHT}拍張照 拍張照
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.52,1:46:47.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness, take a look at this.\N{\rCHT}奈斯 看看這個
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.77,1:46:50.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness?\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.19,1:46:56.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness, are you doing okay? I think you'd better see this.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 你還好吧? 你最好看看這個
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.74,1:47:00.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is it? That's the jury list, Mr Ness.\N{\rCHT}這是什麼 這是陪審團名單
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.83,1:47:02.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,They've been bribed.\N{\rCHT}他們被收買了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.83,1:47:07.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got it out of Nitti's coat. Where is Nitti?\N{\rCHT}從尼蒂西裝裡搜出來的 尼蒂呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.46,1:47:10.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's in the car.\N{\rCHT}他在車上
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.35,1:47:33.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,This constitutes no evidence. I'm not about to allow...\N{\rCHT}這不構成證據 沒有用 我可不准許
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.69,1:47:39.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your Honour, the truth is that Capone is a killer and he will go free.\N{\rCHT}庭上 這案子的事實是 卡彭是個殺人兇手 而你卻要讓他自由
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.64,1:47:44.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,There is only one way to deal with such men, and that is hunt them down.\N{\rCHT}對付他這種人只有一種辦法 便是把他關起來
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.70,1:47:48.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have. I have forsworn myself. I have broken laws I swore to defend.\N{\rCHT}我曾發誓 我要不計任何方法捉住被告
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.00,1:47:53.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,I am content that I have done right. That man must be stopped, you must...\N{\rCHT}我很滿意我所做的正確方法 那個人必須被制止 而你一定要…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.84,1:47:57.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll be the judge of what I must do, Mr Ness.\N{\rCHT}我是法官 我會盡我的責任 奈斯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.27,1:48:10.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you excuse us?\N{\rCHT}請你們出去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.08,1:49:14.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bailiff. Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}法警 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.55,1:49:21.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to go next door to Judge Hoffman's Court,\N{\rCHT}我要你去隔壁霍法官的法庭
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.55,1:49:24.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,where they've just begun hearing a divorce action.\N{\rCHT}他們剛開始審理離婚案件
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.89,1:49:30.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to bring that jury in here and take this jury to his court.\N{\rCHT}我要你把他的陪審團帶來 把這裡的陪審團帶過去
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.94,1:49:35.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are those instructions clear? Yes, sir, they're clear.\N{\rCHT}你聽清楚了嗎 是的 庭上
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.69,1:49:38.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?\N{\rCHT}他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.11,1:49:44.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bailiff, I want you to switch the juries.\N{\rCHT}我要你調換陪審團 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.78,1:49:47.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your Honour, I object!\N{\rCHT}我抗議
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.33,1:49:49.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Overruled.\N{\rCHT}駁回
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.29,1:49:55.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,What did you tell him?\N{\rCHT}你是怎麼說動他的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.88,1:50:00.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told him his name was in the ledger, too.\N{\rCHT}我說他的名字也在帳本上
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.47,1:50:04.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,His name wasn't in the ledger!\N{\rCHT}但他的名字並不在帳本上
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.47,1:50:07.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! Is this the law? What's going on here?\N{\rCHT}等等 這就是法律嗎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.76,1:50:09.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're out of order. What's going on?\N{\rCHT}- 請守秩序 - 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.43,1:50:10.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think...\N{\rCHT}我認為
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.23,1:50:12.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,OK.What you think... Do something here.\N{\rCHT}我不管你認為什麼 想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.98,1:50:15.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do I look like to you? Do something\N{\rCHT}我看起來像什麼? 想點辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.15,1:50:18.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Order!\N{\rCHT}秩序
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.23,1:50:23.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your Honour, we'd like to withdraw our plea of Not Guilty,\N{\rCHT}庭上 我們撤回無罪申辯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.70,1:50:25.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,and enter a plea of Guilty.\N{\rCHT}改為有罪申辯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.24,1:50:32.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Guilty? Order in the court!\N{\rCHT}維持庭上秩序
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.25,1:50:34.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Order!\N{\rCHT}秩序
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.30,1:50:48.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bailiff, clear the courtroom!\N{\rCHT}法警 維持秩序
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.81,1:50:55.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your Honour! Is that justice?\N{\rCHT}庭上 庭上 這公正嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.19,1:50:58.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please, why did he switch the jury?\N{\rCHT}他為何調換陪審團?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.06,1:51:00.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna go after the organisation?\N{\rCHT}你有何打算? 你打算繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.86,1:51:02.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N{\rCHT}借光
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.61,1:51:07.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm asking Your Honour, is this justice?\N{\rCHT}那是公正嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.74,1:51:14.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is this justice?\N{\rCHT}這樣公正嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.33,1:51:20.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Never stop fighting till the fight is done.\N{\rCHT}絕不停止 絕不停止戰鬥 直到戰鬥終止
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.25,1:51:21.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\N{\rCHT}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.96,1:51:25.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,I said, never stop fighting till the fight is done.\N{\rCHT}我說絕不停止戰鬥 直到戰鬥停止為止
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.30,1:51:27.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? You heard me, Capone. It's over.\N{\rCHT}你聽到我的話了 卡彭 都結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.55,1:51:30.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a lot of talk and a badge.\N{\rCHT}滾開 你只會說大話
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.33,1:51:33.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here endeth the lesson.\N{\rCHT}最後一課
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.31,1:51:37.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a lot of talk and a badge!\N{\rCHT}你只知道口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.11,1:51:59.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,“不可動搖者打擊罪犯”
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.38,1:52:04.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,“奈斯保證不被收買”
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.91,1:52:08.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,“卡彭今天出庭”
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.05,1:52:13.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,“卡彭被判十一年徒刑”
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.10,1:53:01.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,So much violence.\N{\rCHT}太多暴力了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.46,1:54:10.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cleaning up a little.\N{\rCHT}總算清理了一點
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.56,1:54:21.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess this is goodbye.\N{\rCHT}我想該說再見了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.89,1:54:24.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, George.\N{\rCHT}再見 喬治
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.11,1:54:30.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to...thank you for this.\N{\rCHT}我要感謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.28,1:54:33.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}不 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.96,1:54:53.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness... I think he would have wanted you to have that.\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 我認為他希望你能保有的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.80,1:54:57.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,He'd have wanted a cop to have it.\N{\rCHT}他希望送給員警
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.51,1:55:03.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.\N{\rCHT}我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.03,1:55:16.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Ness! Any comment for the record?\N{\rCHT}奈斯先生 你對這標題有何意見
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.89,1:55:19.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,'The man who put Al Capone on the spot.'\N{\rCHT}捉拿卡彭下獄的人
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.74,1:55:22.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be there when the wheel went round.\N{\rCHT}我只是適逢其時而已
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.54,1:55:25.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,They say they're going to repeal prohibition.\N{\rCHT}聽說禁酒令將取消
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.75,1:55:29.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,What will you do then? I think I'll have a drink.\N{\rCHT}你會怎麼做? 也許我會去喝上一杯

